31:37.930 --> 31:38.962
- [Nun] Sally?

31:38.964 --> 31:39.663
Sally?!

31:42.067 --> 31:43.100
- Yes?

31:43.102 --> 31:44.134
- The face of who?

31:46.438 --> 31:47.371
- I'm sorry, what?

31:49.575 --> 31:52.376
- Who's face are
they hiding from?

31:56.215 --> 31:57.080
- Satan?

31:58.651 --> 31:59.950
- Incorrect, Sally.

